Set Up Customer Service Incident Management Integrations

Integrate Customer Service Incident Management with partner systems to identify potential issues and proactively address them.

Available in: Lightning Experience with standard Service Cloud license
Available in: Professional, Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

Customer Service Incident Management supports integrations:

Automated Customer Service Incident Management
Cadalys Service Management
Datadog
Jira via MuleSoft Composer (Beta)
PagerDuty
Salesforce Critical Incident Center
ServiceNow via MuleSoft Composer (Beta)

Install AppExchange Integrations

From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Customer Service Incident Management, and then click Customer Service Incident Management.
Under Integrations, choose an integration and install the managed package.

Get started with Customer Service Incident Management integrations that use MuleSoft Composer:

Learn how to use MuleSoft Composer templates.
Contact your Salesforce account executive.
title: Service Cloud Integration Setup and Management
